#: ../../source/cli/quota.rst:2
msgid "lmcache quota"
msgstr "lmcache quota"

#: ../../source/cli/quota.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache quota`` command manages per-salt cache quotas on a running "
"LMCache server. Quotas are soft limits: exceeding a quota triggers "
"eviction on the next cycle (~1 s) rather than rejecting writes."
msgstr "``lmcache quota`` 命令管理运行中的 LMCache 服务器上的每个 salt 的缓存配额。配额是软限制：超过配额会在下一个周期（约 1 秒）触发逐出，而不是拒绝写入。"

